content:
 FAQs # What is Rebuild.Chat? # Rebuild is a Matrix homeserver who believe the current state of events is beyond simple ammendment, hence &ldquo;Rebuild&rdquo;. The topic of most rooms is how to start taking action and planning what needs to be done.
How do I join Rebuild.Chat? # If you already have a Matrix homeserver, you are welcome to join via federation. Otherwise, you can create an account with us as your homeserver (with the option of joining other servers via federation as well).
# Desktop (Rebuild Web Client) Open up your browser of choice to https://rebuild.chat/ Click &ldquo;Create an account&rdquo; Click &ldquo;Continue&rdquo; to bypass the homeserver selection, and fill out the form Mobile (and other third party Matrix clients) Download the client of your choice. I recommend FluffyChat but they all have their tradeoffs. Change homeserver to rebuild.chat Click &ldquo;Create Account&rdquo;
